reviewText: Misleading title of DVD. One Curious George program and a bunch of other junk cartoons.
My 5 month old son loves it

My kids hated it this DVD. They love George the cartoon but there are NO cartoons on this one. There are just told stories with drawn characters, that's it. If you are expecting cartoons get the other DVDs but not this one.

GREAT DVD, MY GRANDDAUGHTER LOVES IT AND CAN'T WATCH IT ENOUGH.

THANKS SO MUCH

Personally, i really like the newer Curious George series, but someone bought this one for my kids and they really love it.  It's the old fashioned type of book animation, with non-moving pictures and a narrator telling the story, but, hey, my kids don't seem to care.  There are a few other books on this dvd as well, they are cute stories, but don't seem to hold my kids' interest for very long.
